headline: Billionaire Investor Bill Ackman Just Went All In on This Stock. Should You Follow Suit?
summary: Billionaire investor Bill Ackman made Uber his largest holding in Q1.  Uber has been showing solid growth and generating strong free cash flow.  Billionaire investor Bill Ackman made a splash in the first quarter when he took a new position in ride-share company Uber Technologies (NYSE: UBER), making it his largest holding in the process.
